- Commercial use: Any commercial use of content from this platform is prohibited, including but not limited to sales, advertising, and paid access

引用格式建议 | Suggested Citation Format:

[序号] 作者. 文章题目[EB/OL]. 电子游戏科学与技术， 出版日期. 获取或访问路径.

[Number] Author(s). Title[EB/OL]. Journal of E-Gaming Science & Technology, Publication Date. Access Path.

