[2] Li Yutong, Zhao Yifan, Sun Liren. The Impact of Gamified Learning on Adolescent Programming Education: An Empirical Study Based on Meta-Analysis[EB/OL]. Journal of E-Gaming Science & Technology, 2026-01-20. https://journalofest.netlify.app/paper/gamification-programming-meta-analysis


